headline: How UnitedHealth’s CEO Role Split Proposal Impacts the Stock’s Current Value
summary: Deciding what to do with UnitedHealth Group stock right now? You are definitely not alone. After a rocky year filled with both headlines and price swings, investors are eyeing every movement for clues about what might come next. UnitedHealth’s stock has clawed back a bit recently, up 0.6% in the past week and 4.4% this past month. Yet the numbers over the past year remain a sober reminder of what has changed, with the stock down about 36% over twelve months and nearly 30% lower...
